<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="colour-n">colo(u)r <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kʌlə(r)/    美 /'kʌlər/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U]  颜色；色彩：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>warm / cold colours
暖/冷色</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 彩色：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Do you want to print the photo <strong>in colour</strong> or black and white?
你想把照片打印成彩色的还是黑白的？</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c-u">3.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 肤色；脸色；血色：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>people of all colours
各种肤色的人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A glass of wine brought some colour to her cheeks.
喝了杯葡萄酒，让她的脸颊泛起红晕。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As her illness got worse she lost more and more colour.
随着病情加重，她的脸色越来越苍白。</p></div>

